	<div class=\"wp-block-navigation__responsive-dialog\" aria-label=\"Menu\">\n							<button aria-label=\"Tutup menu\" data-micromodal-close class=\"wp-block-navigation__responsive-container-close\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><path d=\"M13 11.8l6.1-6.3-1-1-6.1 6.2-6.1-6.2-1 1 6.1 6.3-6.5 6.7 1 1 6.5-6.6 6.5 6.6 1-1z\"></path></svg></button>\n						<div class=\"wp-block-navigation__responsive-container-content\" id=\"modal-1-content\">\n							<ul class=\"wp-block-navigation__container\"><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/themes/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Tema</span></a></li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/plugins/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Plugin</span></a></li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/news/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Berita</span></a></li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/support/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Bantuan</span></a></li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/about/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Tentang</span></a></li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"/team\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Komunitas</span></a></li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/polyglots/teams/?locale=id_ID\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Poliglot</span></a></li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item global-header__mobile-get-wordpress global-header__get-wordpress wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/download/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Gunakan WordPress</span></a></li></ul>\n						</div>\n					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div></nav>\n\n	\n	<!-- This is the first of two Get WordPress buttons; the other is in the navigation menu.\n		 Two are needed because they have different DOM hierarchies at different breakpoints. -->\n	\n	<div class=\"is-layout-flow global-header__desktop-get-wordpress-container\">\n		<a href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/download/\" class=\"global-header__desktop-get-wordpress global-header__get-wordpress\">\n			Gunakan WordPress		</a>\n	</div> \n</header> \n	<aside id=\"download-mobile\">\n		<span class=\"download-ready\">Siap untuk memulai?</span><a class=\"button download-button\" href=\"/download/\">Instal WordPress</a>\n	</aside>\n\n	<header id=\"masthead\" class=\"site-header\" role=\"banner\">\n		<div class=\"site-branding\">\n			<p class=\"site-title\">Kenali WordPress</p>\n\n			<p class=\"site-description\">WordPress adalah sebuah perangkat lunak open source yang dapat Anda gunakan untuk membuat situs web yang menarik, blog, atau aplikasi.</p>\n		</div><!-- .site-branding -->\n	</header><!-- #masthead -->\n\n	<main id=\"main\" class=\"site-main \" role=\"main\">\n		<div class=\"home-welcome\">\n			<div id=\"lang-guess-wrap\"></div>\n\n			<section class=\"intro\">\n				<p class=\"subheading\">Desain menarik, fitur andal, dan kebebasan untuk menciptakan apa pun yang Anda inginkan. WordPress tersedia gratis, akan tetapi juga tidak ternilai.</p>\n				<div class=\"screenshots\">\n					<img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/home/screen-themes.png?4\" class=\"dashboard\" />\n					<img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/home/mobile-themes.png?4\" class=\"dashboard-mobile\" />\n				</div>\n			</section>\n\n			<section class=\"showcase\">\n				<h2>Dipercaya oleh yang Terbaik</h2>\n				<p class=\"subheading\">\n					43% dari situs web memakai WordPress, mulai dari blog individu hingga portal berita terbesar.				</p>\n				<div class=\"collage\">\n\n				</div>\n				<p class=\"cta-link\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/showcase/\">Temukan situs yang dibangun dengan WordPress</a></p>\n			</section>\n\n			<section class=\"features\">\n				<h2>Fitur yang Andal</h2>\n				<p class=\"subheading\">Potensi tak terbatas. Apa yang ingin Anda ciptakan?</p>\n				<ul>\n					<li>\n						<span class=\"dashicons dashicons-admin-customizer\"></span>\n						Desain<br />Fleksibel					</li>\n					<li>\n						<span class=\"dashicons dashicons-welcome-widgets-menus\"></span>\n						SEO<br />Friendly					</li>\n					<li>\n						<span class=\"dashicons dashicons-smartphone\"></span>\n						Situs Seluler yang<br />Responsif					</li>\n					<li>\n						<span class=\"dashicons dashicons-chart-line\"></span>\n						Performa<br />Tinggi					</li>\n					<li>\n						<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/mobile/\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/home/icon-run-blue.svg\" />\n							Kelola<br />dari Mana Saja</a>\n					</li>\n					<li>\n						<span class=\"dashicons dashicons-lock\"></span>\n						Keamanan<br />Terbaik					</li>\n					<li>\n						<span class=\"dashicons dashicons-images-alt2\"></span>\n						Pengelola<br />Berkas Hebat					</li>\n					<li>\n						<span class=\"dashicons dashicons-universal-access\"></span>\n						Mudah dan<br />Terjangkau					</li>\n				</ul>\n				<p>\n					Kembangkan WordPress dengan lebih dari 55.000 plugin untuk membangun situs sesuai kebutuhan. Tambahkan toko online, galeri, milis, forum, perangkat analitik, dan <a href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/plugins/\">lainnya</a>.				</p>\n			</section>\n\n			<section class=\"community-2\">\n				<div class=\"screen\"></div>\n				<div class=\"container\">\n					<h2>Komunitas</h2>\n					<p class=\"subheading\">\n						Ratusan ribu developer, pembuat konten, dan pemilik situs berkumpul dalam pertemuan bulanan yang diadakan di 817 kota di seluruh dunia.					</p>\n					<a class=\"button button-secondary button-large\" href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/community/meetups-landing-page\">Temukan komunitas WordPress di sekitarmu</a>\n				</div>\n			</section>\n\n			<section class=\"get\">\n				<h2>Mulai Menggunakan WordPress</h2>\n				<p class=\"subheading\">Lebih dari 60 juta orang telah memilih WordPress untuk mewujudkan tempat yang mereka sebut &ldquo;rumah&rdquo; di jaringan internet &mdash; bergabunglah bersama keluarga besar WordPress.</p>\n				<div class=\"cta-wrapper\">\n					<a href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/download/\" class=\"button button-primary button-xl\">Instal WordPress</a>\n				</div>\n			</section>\n		</div>\n\n		<div id=\"home-below\" class=\"home-below row gutters\">\n			<div class=\"col-4\">\n				<h4><a href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/news/\">Kabar Terkini</a></h4><h5><a href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/2021/08/28/wordpress-translation-day-2021-ayo-terjemahkan-plugin-wordpress-paling-populer/\" rel=\"bookmark\">WordPress Translation Day 2021 – Ayo terjemahkan plugin WordPress paling populer!</a></h5><div class=\"entry-summary\"><p>Tim WordPress Polyglots akan melaksanakan sebuah kegiatan yang bertajuk WordPress Translation Day 2021 selama satu bulan penuh pada September 2021. Kegiatan tersebut diselenggarakan untuk ikut berpartisipasi merayakan “Hari Penerjemahan Internasional” yang jatuh pada setiap tanggal 30 September. Melanjutkan kegiatan tahun lalu, Jakarta WordPress Meetup bekerja sama dengan Poliglot WordPress Indonesia akan mengadakan kegiatan kolaborasi daring [&hellip;]</p>\n</div>			</div>\n\n			<div class=\"col-4\">\n				<h4>Sangat Mudah&hellip;</h4>\n\n				<ol class=\"steps\">\n					<li class=\"one\">\n						<span></span>\n						<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/hosting/\">Temukan penyedia hosting terpercaya</a> dan juga dukung WordPress.					</li>\n					<li class=\"two\">\n						<span></span>\n						<a href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/download/\">Unduh &amp; instal WordPress</a> dengan instalasi 5-menit kami yang terkenal. Cara termudah untuk memublikasikan konten Anda.					</li>\n					<li class=\"three\">\n						<span></span>\n						<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/\">Luangkan waktu Anda untuk membaca dokumentasi kami</a>, pelajari  WordPress lebih jauh setiap hari dan bantu pengguna lain,&nbsp;.					</li>\n				</ol>\n			</div>\n\n			<div class=\"col-4 first\">\n				<h4><a href=\"https://mercantile.wordpress.org/\">Swag&nbsp;WordPress</a></h4>\n				<a href=\"https://mercantile.wordpress.org/\">\n											<img width=\"288\" height=\"288\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/home/swag_col-2.png\" srcset=\"https://s.w.org/images/home/swag_col-2_x2.png 2x\" alt=\"Swag WordPress\" />\n									</a>\n			</div>\n\n			<div class=\"col-12\">\n				<h4><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/showcase/\">Para Pengguna WordPress</a></h4>\n\n									<div id=\"notable-users\" class=\"notable-users col-12 row gutters\">\n						<div class=\"col-3\"><a href=\"https://persija.id/\"><img src=\"https://wordpress.com/mshots/v1/https%3A%2F%2Fpersija.id%2F?w=220\" width=\"220\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Persija Jakarta\" /></a></div><div class=\"col-3\"><a href=\"http://slank.com\"><img src=\"https://wordpress.com/mshots/v1/http%3A%2F%2Fslank.com?w=220\" width=\"220\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Slank Band\" /></a></div><div class=\"col-3\"><a href=\"https://data.go.id/\"><img src=\"https://wordpress.com/mshots/v1/https%3A%2F%2Fdata.go.id%2F?w=220\" width=\"220\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Portal Data Indonesia\" /></a></div><div class=\"col-3\"><a href=\"https://dailysocial.id/\"><img src=\"https://wordpress.com/mshots/v1/https%3A%2F%2Fdailysocial.id%2F?w=220\" width=\"220\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"DailySocial\" /></a></div>					</div>\n				\n				<a class=\"showcase-link\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/showcase/\">&hellip; dan ratusan lainnya</a>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n\n	</main><!-- #main -->\n\n\n\n\n<footer class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group alignfull global-footer  has-text-color has-background has-white-color has-charcoal-2-background-color\">\n	\n	<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group global-footer__navigation-container\">\n		<nav class=\"is-layout-flex global-footer__navigation-important wp-block-navigation\" aria-label=\"\"><ul class=\"wp-block-navigation__container\"><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/about/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Tentang</span></a></li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/news/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Berita</span></a></li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://wordpress.org/hosting/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Hosting</span></a></li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://wordpressfoundation.org/donate/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Donasi</span></a></li></ul></nav>\n\n		<nav class=\"is-layout-flex global-footer__navigation-information wp-block-navigation\" aria-label=\"\"><ul class=\"wp-block-navigation__container\"><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://id.wordpress.org/support/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Bantuan</span></a></li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https://develope